src:
ورود سرزده گوزن به آرایشگاه

02 Nov 2019, 14:01

ورود ناگهانی یک گوزن به آرایشگاهی در آمریکا موجب وحشت یکی از کارکنان شد. مدتی پیش همین اتفاق در آرایشگاهی دیگر در نیویورک افتاد.
text:
Know this Saturday's Totoloto Keys
Chamber of Machico approves Municipal Budget of 10.1 ME with votes in favor of the PS

02 Nov 2019, 14:49




Today was another draw of Totoloto, whose key extracted resulted in the numbers 8, 13, 14, 27 and 39, with the supplementary number 9.
Please note that prizes awarded in excess of 5,000.00 euros are subject to stamp duty at the legal rate of 20%, in accordance with the legislation in force.
This was the draw # 088/2019.
